name: Barack Obama Limited Edition Black T-shirt
description:
Tell America to wake up and Stop the Drama, Vote Obama with this awesome Limited Edition t-shirt from the new Radical Left Wing Liberal clothing company, Dead Elephant.
Stop the Dram Vote Obama T-shirt includes a huge multi color printed graphic, with printed inside Dead Elephant Seal of Disapproval label. Obama T-shirt is available in S, M, L, XL. & XXL Only 75 Shirts were produced of this style. Once their gone, their gone!
Some proceeds from t-shirt purchase will go to the Obama for President Campaign Free Vinyl Dead Elephant Seal of Disapproval stickers with every Tee Shirt purchase.
Learn more about Dead Elephant Clothing at: http://www.myspace.com/deadelephantclothing
